\begin_layout Standard
Given a unit quaternion 
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

 with scalar part 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

 and vector part 
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

.
 Then, rotation matrix can be found as
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\family roman
\series medium
\shape up
\size normal
\emph off
\bar no
\strikeout off
\xout off
\uuline off
\uwave off
\noun off
